{"tid":2094792,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"薩滿/醫療靈媒/文王殿/音叉/生物共振/髗骶骨用家請進tg gp比意見,不能上學/班,病8年,腹瀉,手腳無力,25歲胖男","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:49:45.000Z","uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de235ca5a81aafb526c9c281d158d5464595ed68","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"不能上學/班，病齡8年，腹瀉，手腳無力，25歲胖男<br />\n<br />\n主訴：<br />\n我的蛋白質類攝取中只選極低脂的食物，如雞胸、極低脂魚柳、蝦。如食物中脂肪比例增加，如生牛肉湯濛（營養師建議吃），吃了有機會肚痛/腹瀉/&ldquo;濟&rdquo;/大便爛（以往出現，現在不敢吃，不確定）。<br />\n<br />\n現史：<br />\n手腳無力至不能自理（程度：煮一人餐），職業治療師診斷我手做重複性動作會累<br />\n手指耐力低<br />\n曾吃粗糧，肚臍上9cm位置頂<br />\n曾吃冷物，會覺得肚很冷<br />\n手腳掌出汗，手腳掌冰冷，腳板脫皮<br />\n小便分差，陽痿（連皮/剝皮香蕉硬度）<br />\n<br />\n往史:<br />\n09年9月-11年5月，曾常吃龜苓膏、飲涼茶，以防暗瘡，現回頭看不應吃。有手淫習慣<br />\n12年9月開始手腳無力至今<br />\n14年5月開始嚴重<br />\n6,7月很疲勞仍勉強上學/班，結果更疲勞<br />\n9月起經常腹瀉<br />\n<br />\n西醫:<br />\n精神科開了aripiprazole 5mg sertraline (hcl) 50mg 每日各半粒，像有用，驗證中<br />\n腦神經內科做了神經傳導檢查，排除了重症肌無力，問他有甚麼其他檢查可做，他說無。<br />\n內分泌科排除了Cushing's syndrome。<br />\n照過胸背頸x光。 <br />\n14年驗出肝酵素高。 <br />\n17年照胃鏡，有胃炎。 脂肪肝。<br />\n運動後更疲勞<br />\n<br />\n順勢療法：sulphur q1像有用，驗證中<br />\n<br />\n中醫：<br />\n基本上以以下路線醫好一半，-代表藥後反應<br />\n參苓白朮散-止瀉、有力＞平胃散-大便變完整＞右歸丸贊育丹減約半熟地-吃油少少較不易肚屙＞便秘之後就睇黃志忠-好亂手寫個張＞十全大補-有力<br />\n另外：<br />\n補中益氣湯-有力<br />\n<br />\n病人資料、問診單、舊中藥、順勢處方：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffolderview%3Fid%3D1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=2479f04f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU</a><br />\n<br />\n無：食物敏感<br />\n<br />\n家人病歷：<br />\n父：痔瘡<br />\n母：乙型肝炎、小腸氣、割掉口水線有粒嘢<br />\n兄：無<br />\n<br />\ntg group/ tg(最活躍平台):<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=a4b1dad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=400c3484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a><br />\n<br />\nfb page/ messager:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E8%B7%AA%E6%B1%82%E7%A5%9E%E9%86%AB%E7%97%85%E9%BD%A18%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%9B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD25%E6%AD%B2%E8%83%96%E7%94%B7-100320258254152/?ref=bookmarks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%25BD%25A18%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%258F%25AD25%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%2583%2596%25E7%2594%25B7-100320258254152%2F%3Fref%3Dbookmarks&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=0c6a9685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E8%B7%AA%E6%B1%82%E7%A5%9E%E9%86%AB%E7%97%85%E9%BD%A18%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%9B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD25%E6%AD%B2%E8%83%96%E7%94%B7-100320258254152/?ref=bookmarks</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=a7a8a749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\n<br />\n跪求介紹治療師<br />\n請問<br />\n1.他有沒醫好過我的主訴？<br />\n2.他有沒醫好過手腳無力及不能自理（程度不能煮一人餐）？<br />\n3.他醫好過甚麼棘手個案<br />\n4.介不介意分享你甚麼病<br />\n5.你病了多長時間才醫好？<br />\n<br />\n待辦診治：要求西醫照腦<br />\n髗骶骨療法<br />\n音叉<br />\n接地氣<br />\n薩滿<br />\n鍾灼輝潛醫識能量療法<br />\n吳神父按摩<br />\n<br />\n不知如何找：醫療靈媒<br />\n<br />\n未試，不覺得有用：原始點<br />\n文王殿"},{"pid":"c849b009a14784165af43ebafd88eae6dc61a3a3","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"8d058750d52c675f2c0152f755aa59049fc9ac3e","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"96ddf4e994c9602798121d2aa597d24dcd5f3c4f","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"6f72b3dac9f323cb229598e344febd9eae90335b","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"142b1924ad0002b56225f10c92badff3b55eeb33","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"8b07c6d3bb78c1d60c27c315d2fa75d322c3d7e4","tid":2094792,"uid":224020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"你肝酵素高有冇試過照膽？<br />\n有可能有膽石"},{"pid":"5f45854c8aefdaf2879a9c2476dbc7d703337bb2","tid":2094792,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b07c6d3bb78c1d60c27c315d2fa75d322c3d7e4","tid":2094792,"uid":224020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"你肝酵素高有冇試過照膽？<br />\n有可能有膽石"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"0c37f5ea30cdb971e7da0cc28b120d878fe33729","tid":2094792,"uid":106633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"你似有精神病多啲"},{"pid":"ae4eb0a938fd227af2a3467cdb4982f3bb1f90b0","tid":2094792,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老味問咁多年都夠你考個醫生番黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058aece478b237e84f3c7374be725e80bae33743","tid":2094792,"uid":190264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote